title: WWE/WWF Survivor Series 2001
description:
Survivor Series 2001 was the fifteenth annual Survivor Series pay-per-view professional wrestling event produced by the World Wrestling Federation. It took place on November 18, 2001 at the Greensboro Coliseum in Greensboro, North Carolina. The official theme song was \"Control\", by Puddle of Mudd.

The Invasion angle ended at this event with the \"Winner Take All Match.\"

Matches:

Christian vs Al Snow (European Title)

William Regal vs Tajiri (w/Torrie Wilson)

Test vs Edge (WCW United States Title & WWF Intercontinental Title Unification Match)

The Dudley Boyz (w/Stacey Keibler) vs The Hardy Boyz (Steel Cage) (WWF Tag Team Titles & WCW Tag Team Titles Unification Match)

Billy Gunn; Bradshaw; Faarooq; Lance Storm; Billy Kidman; Diamond Dallas Page; Albert; Tazz; Perry Saturn; Raven; Test; Chuck Palumbo; Crash Holly; Justin Credible; Shawn Stasiak; Steven Richards; Tommy Dreamer; The Hurricane; Spike Dudley; Hugh Morrus; Chavo Guerrero, Jr.; and Funaki. (Immunity Battle Royal)

Trish Stratus; Jacqueline; Lita; Ivory; Mighty Molly and Jazz (Six Pack Challenge) (WWF Womens Title)

Team Alliance (Shane Mcmahon; Booker T; Rob Van Dam; Kurt Angle & Stone Cold Steve Austin) vs Team WWF (Big Show; Kane; The Undertaker; Chris Jericho & The Rock) (Winner Takes All Survivor Series match)
